{"tid":2188184,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(懶人徐晃) 自製吉野家牛肉飯","createTime":"2020-09-04T05:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T12:32:18.000Z","uid":314521,"like":6,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"21233eb0635966fe7a22163e4d86ca2002da219b","tid":2188184,"uid":314521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:32:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最近我超鍾意煮啲日本野  所以今日我決定整<br />\n <strong>吉野家牛肉飯</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前好多位巴絲都整過 所以我就直接PO相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">肥牛就基本野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/027jpvB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F027jpvB.jpg&h=55cf4368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">洋蔥同薑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkHzdpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkHzdpG.jpg&h=24ea0a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">整一整個牛汁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eK5dtYB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeK5dtYB.jpg&h=21e8c865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UaGXbbX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaGXbbX.jpg&h=82b1e5f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">跟住開始整熟啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2zahbcs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zahbcs.jpg&h=546e8626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">見啲洋蔥差唔多熟就落肥牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3HvwcR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3HvwcR.jpg&h=5cb1aaba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EL6XbcS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEL6XbcS.jpg&h=e5af3798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">食得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8kUdrH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8kUdrH.jpg&h=80b8f8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vomwfE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvomwfE3.jpg&h=4cca0f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">好味</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"xx-large\">懶人一定要學</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ceff2135e81f4edce93f33649eaf7abda10dba","tid":2188184,"uid":239912,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:34:08.000Z","msg":"睇樣柴到仆街喎"},{"pid":"1bde7bbc706cb1ec508f25440e8c86bf19605fed","tid":2188184,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:34:11.000Z","msg":"牛冇乜肥肉<br />\nfail<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a0389191f5fc3caaeee588225dddd1681